Test fixtures
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The offline fixtures under tests/fixtures/ are captures from a Hitachi VSP
*training simulator*, never a production array. Every identifier in them is
synthetic: serial numbers are placeholder values, and IP addresses use the
RFC 5737 documentation range (192.0.2.0/24). No customer or production data is
present anywhere in this repository.
